{"type": "article", "id": 12802, "title": "Manolo Blahnik 包袋系列", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-30T07:50:43Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 6, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000203NGImSAJDZaEPUe51.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t你有没有想过 Manolo Blahnik 变成包会是什么样子？这个酷酷的品牌 Manolo Blahnik 最近宣布要开始做包了，他们将会在这个月月底推出晚装包系列，会延续高跟鞋的风格，且共享设计风格。目前我们看到的预告里面，包包仍然走的华美路线。全线产品将会在明年春天发布，价格在 2000 美元左右。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261405021wp2qAeiPYUGyVJt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50093809\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140503ULVHKOnmQGohIfJp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50093809\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140503XMvVcEmYQGdFWkbT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50093809\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140504urY8tCljqxef5Eai.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50093809\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}